    busy-waits for the response, and returns the verification result.
</verbatim></para><para><simplesect kind="return"><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS, if LMS signature verification KAT passes.</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_FAILURE, if the KAT fails. </para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
<para>Configure LMS signature verification parameters using KAT vectors.</para><para>Configure client parameters for synchronous operation.</para><para>Send LMS signature verification request to ASUFW.</para><para>Busy-wait for ASUFW response.</para><para>Check verification status from callback. </para>        </inbodydescription>
